{"content": "<p>Geodetic Moments features 100 photographs captured 'in absentia'. </p><p>Each Geodetic Moment places the viewer at the centre of a world where a person that is loved is absent.</p><p>You cannot forget them, yet you cannot move on either.</p><p>You may <em><em>know</em></em> that person. You may <em><em>be</em></em> that person.</p><p>Geodetic Moments create a place and a space to feel a temporary sense of respite from the absence. Explore the many emotions that comes from loss through the lens of a single vantage point.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/geodetic-moments\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">View Geodetic Moments Collection on OpenSea</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/geodetic-banner-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1_geodetic-banner-1.png 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/geodetic-banner-1.png 1000w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/geodetic-banner-1.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>There is also a dedicated website <a href=\"https://www.geodeticmoments.com\">geodeticmoments.com</a> that goes deeper into each artwork, <a href=\"https://www.geodeticmoments.com/navigating-the-collection/\">navigating the traits</a> and how to <a href=\"https://www.geodeticmoments.com/participate/\">participate in your country</a> if it speaks to you.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.geodeticmoments.com\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">View Geodetic Moments collection</a></div><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"You might see one person in the distance on the path. That is enough to know you are not alone.\"</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/61-1200x675.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1_61.jpg 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2_61.jpg 1000w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/3_61-1200x675.jpg 1600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/4_61-1200x675.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/100151078309057675366159992497543003968848618159963270405575559582233279856641\">Geodetic Moment #61</a> on OpenSea</figcaption></figure><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"Strength is at the core.\"</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/86-1200x675.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1_86.jpg 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2_86.jpg 1000w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/3_86-1200x675.jpg 1600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/4_86-1200x676.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@mintface/foundation/132520\">Geodetic Moment #86</a> on Foundation</figcaption></figure><p>#86 got sent to the burnt address to be reminted as <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@mintface/foundation/132520\">'Geodetic Moment'</a> on Foundation. It is the apex moment of the collection.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/69-1200x675.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1_69.jpg 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2_69.jpg 1000w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/3_69-1200x675.jpg 1600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/4_69-1200x675.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>Geodetic Moment #69 on OpenSea</figcaption></figure><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"Remember to focus in on the details.\"</blockquote><p>#69 is the first photo I looked at in Lightroom and thought 'yeah, this is the aesthetic for the Geodetic Moment narrative'.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">▲ Geodetic Moments is now LIVE<a href=\"https://t.co/SHUf0b3FJg\">https://t.co/SHUf0b3FJg</a><br /><br />100 geodetic moments photographed in absentia. <a href=\"https://t.co/ZGBO6G0eGB\">pic.twitter.com/ZGBO6G0eGB</a></p>&mdash; MintFace 🍒 (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1494153837523120133?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 17, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>The <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/geodetic-moments\">Geodetic Moments collection</a> was created by MintFace over the last six months, beginning during 'JPEG summer' of 2021 and completing on Wednesday 16th February 2022.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">If you are catching up on Geodetic Moments…<br /><br />🍒 100 photographs by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mintfaced</a> <br />🍒 170 days starting JPEG summer 2021 <br />🍒 floor resets to 0.05 in 24 hours<br /><br />14 SALES in the last 12 hours!! 🤯🤯🤯<br /><br />Collection website launched Wednesday<a href=\"https://t.co/SHUf0aLwv8\">https://t.co/SHUf0aLwv8</a></p>&mdash; MintFace 🍒 (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1494414774175625230?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 17, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p></p><hr /><p>Receive new artist features by email.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-left\"><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Subscribe to MintFace</a></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-callout-card kg-callout-card-pink\"><div class=\"kg-callout-emoji\">💡</div><div class=\"kg-callout-text\"><strong>Artists. Join the next <a href=\"https://maven.com/mintface/nft-digital-artist-economy\">Digital Artist Economy Accelerator</a> </strong>and launch your NFT collection with confidence on your own smart contract.</div></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-callout-card kg-callout-card-purple\"><div class=\"kg-callout-emoji\">💡</div><div class=\"kg-callout-text\"><strong>Collectors. </strong><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup\">Subscribe to MintFace Premium</a> for $USD9 per month. MintFace surfaces great artists and artworks so you don't have to.</div></div><p></p><p></p>"}